meanings: [Noun] labelenfiguratively perfection on a literal or metaphorical scale of 0-10, where 10 is the qualitatively the best outcome; a perfect specimen, especially one who is physically attractive
[Noun] (video games) A category in that pertains to the goal of completing the game while also everything possible.
[Adjective] Alternative form of one hundred percent
[Adverb] Alternative form of one hundred percent
